title: Weekend crisis looms for leader of Taiwan's floundering ruling party
text:
Published By: Reuters - World news - Today 
TAIPEI (Reuters) - Taiwan's panicked ruling Nationalists party will likely ditch its candidate for January's presidential election this week...
